  npcName: Loveland Frog
  _npcRating: 0
  _isFinalNode: 0
  _lines:
  - Watchu lookin' at, hot stuff?
  - Him and I go way back, you know.
  - He may not seem like it, but the old bastard's tough as nails.
  - He'll be back on his feet in no time.
  - I mean he has to be...
  - He doesn't really got other limbs.
  - So how 'bout you forget about that prick so we can get down on some real fun...
  _playerReplyOptions:
  - Sorry I'm on business.
  - What kind of fun?
  - I wanna know more about you two.
